==English==

===Pronunciation===
*[[Pronunciation guide|IPA]]:/fɪə/, /fir/

===Noun===
'''fear''' (''plural:'' '''[[fears]]''')

#(''uncountable'') An uncontrollable [[emotion]] of [[anxiety]] about something that causes a [[scared]] reaction or [[frightening]] impression. 
#*He was struck by fear on seeing the snake.
#The [[emotion|emotions]] induced by a particular frightening entity.
#* Not everybody has the same '''fears'''.
#*I have a fear of [[:w:ants|ants]].

